apps.name: Instagram Rocket
apps.subtitle: Instagram 145.0 | Rocket 3.7.3 | NoAds
apps.localizedDescription: Instagram Rocket is an amazing tweak by Majd Alfhaily which adds a bunch of amazing and useful new features to Instagram. By default, there are a lot of features that users crave to see on the Instagram app. These features might never see the light of the day, but Instagram Rocket aims to tackle this issue by bringing some of the most requested features to Instagram.
